---
import CTAButton from "../ui/CTAButton.astro";
import NavigationHint from "../ui/NavigationHint.astro";
---

<!-- About Section -->
<section
  id="about"
  class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative"
>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-8">About Tam</h2>
    <div class="prose prose-lg sm:prose-xl prose-invert max-w-none mb-12">
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-6">
        I recognize you as a growing being—someone already able to engage in good
        philosophic conversation, whether you call it that or not. You arrive
        with standing, not as someone who needs fixing.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-6">
        I'm not here to give advice, assess how you're doing, or offer a
        diagnosis. As your philosophical counselor, I am an ally in
        your growth, work, and learning—a power listener who takes your mind
        seriously. I can help you realize, solidify, and integrate the wisdom
        you've already gleaned, what you already know deep down.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-400 mb-6">
        Certified by
        <a
          href="https://appa.edu/about/"
          class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 underline">APPA</a
        >
        (the American Philosophical Practitioners Association). With a background in
        software development, I've built custom infrastructure that transforms
        our conversations into AI-optimized transcripts—bridging ancient wisdom
        with tools for ongoing exploration.
      </p>
      <blockquote class="text-2xl font-medium italic border-none">
        "You arrive with standing, not as someone who needs fixing"
      </blockquote>
    </div>

    <!-- Let's talk CTA -->
    <div class="mt-8 text-center">
      <CTAButton variant="secondary" />
    </div>

    <NavigationHint href="#process" text="What to expect" />
  </div>
</section>
